				<title>K8s（十）：Helm 包管理器入门</title>
				<link>https://liwenqikeep.github.io/posts/k8s%E5%8D%81helm-%E5%8C%85%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%99%A8%E5%85%A5%E9%97%A8/</link>
